  "texts": [
    "The question of whether current evaluation practices for SA are still applicable in the era of LLMs was also raised.",
    "The performance was evaluated across 13 tasks on 26 datasets.",
    "The LLMs and SLMs were as follows:",
    "• Large language models (LLMs) LLMs refer to large-scale language models, such as GPT-3.",
    "These models utilize the Transformer architecture, possess many parameters and pretraining data, and perform excellently in various natural language processing tasks."
  ]
}